org.gbif.metrics.cube.mapred

Class OccurrenceWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.metrics.cube.mapred.OccurrenceWritable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<OccurrenceWritable>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<OccurrenceWritable>

    public class OccurrenceWritable
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<OccurrenceWritable>
    A container object for use in MR, that encapsulates the fields needed to locate similar records at the same point. Effectively this is analogous to set of GROUP BY fields.
